{"id":101,"name":"القارعة","transliteration":"Al-Qari'ah","type":"meccan","total_verses":11,"verses":[{"id":1,"ar":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","tr":"AlqariAAatu","tr_readable":"Al qaari'ah","tr_academic":"al-qāriʿatu","de":"Das Verhängnis"},{"id":2,"ar":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","tr":"Ma alqariAAatu","tr_readable":"Mal qaariah","tr_academic":"mā l-qāriʿatu","de":"Was ist das Verhängnis"},{"id":3,"ar":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","tr":"Wama adraka ma alqariAAatu","tr_readable":"Wa maa adraaka mal qaari'ah","tr_academic":"wamā adrāka mā l-qāriʿatu","de":"Und was läßt dich wissen, was das Verhängnis ist"},{"id":4,"ar":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","tr":"Yawma yakoonu alnnasu kaalfarashi almabthoothi","tr_readable":"Yauma ya koonun naasu kal farashil mabthooth","tr_academic":"yawma yakūnu l-nāsu kal-farāshi l-mabthūthi","de":"Am Tag, da die Menschen wie flatternde Motten sein werden"},{"id":5,"ar":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","tr":"Watakoonu aljibalu kaalAAihni almanfooshi","tr_readable":"Wa ta koonul jibalu kal 'ihnil manfoosh","tr_academic":"watakūnu l-jibālu kal-ʿih'ni l-manfūshi","de":"und die Berge wie zerflockte gefärbte Wolle sein werden"},{"id":6,"ar":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","tr":"Faamma man thaqulat mawazeenuhu","tr_readable":"Fa-amma man thaqulat mawa zeenuh","tr_academic":"fa-ammā man thaqulat mawāzīnuhu","de":"Was nun jemanden angeht, dessen Waagschalen schwer sind"},{"id":7,"ar":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","tr":"Fahuwa fee AAeeshatin radiyatin","tr_readable":"Fahuwa fee 'ishatir raadiyah","tr_academic":"fahuwa fī ʿīshatin rāḍiyatin","de":"so wird er in einem zufriedenen Leben sein"},{"id":8,"ar":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","tr":"Waamma man khaffat mawazeenuhu","tr_readable":"Wa amma man khaffat mawa zeenuh","tr_academic":"wa-ammā man khaffat mawāzīnuhu","de":"Was aber jemanden angeht, dessen Waagschalen leicht sind"},{"id":9,"ar":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","tr":"Faommuhu hawiyatun","tr_readable":"Fa-ummuhu